in a new president 
his voice turned raspy and he apologized to an audience of 
sailors in norfolk va tuesday for just croaking away on 
wednesday he lost his voice altogether to laryngitis and greeted 
guests at a diplomatic reception that night in a bare whisper he 
canceled a speech looked flushed said he was taking antibiotics 
