admiral during the russojapanese war who commanded the interception 
and destruction of the russian baltic fleet in the battle of 
tsushima in 1905 
togo was in charge of educating hirohito from 1914 until 1924 
and was known for his loyalty to the monarchy he died in 1934 
the shrine is located less than a mile from the site where 
hirohitos state funeral will be held feb 24 
