crashed in bad weather near clear lake iowa en route to a concert 
date in fargo nd 
at the time holly was a giant on the fledgling rocknroll scene 
and his death became known as the day the music died valens was 
a budding star famous for his hit la bamba 
richardson who was from beaumont was known as the big 
