arctic air blasted its way into the northeast and texas on 
friday bringing widespread freezing rain 
belowzero temperatures spread as far south as northern oklahoma 
and the texas panhandle temperatures fell to 30 below zero or 
colder from northern minnesota across parts of the dakotas to 
