retailers however most said thursday in reporting january sales 
that they benefited from light inventories and an unusually warm 
winter 
the low inventory levels due to unexpectedly brisk christmas 
business and tight control of stocks saved general merchandise and 
apparel retailers from having to slash prices to move out the excess 
goods 
patterns of retail purchases are closely watched for indications 
of overall consumer spending which accounts for twothirds of the 
countrys overall economic activity 
