maine maine public service co bangor hydroelectric co of maine 
and central vermont public service co ashooh said public service 
also would waive 800000 in debt from central maine 
those companies sold their seabrook shares totaling 12 percent 
of the project to a subsidiary of eastern utilities associates of 
massachusetts in 1986 
