deal as it asked yacos for another extension of the deadline for the 
projects past and present owners to file claims against it in 
bankruptcy court 
yacos previously had granted three extensions of the deadline for 
claims against public service and said last month there would be 
no further extensions beyond feb 9 but on friday he granted 
one more extension to feb 24 
